getRelatedVersions

public int[] getRelatedVersions(java.lang.String relatedStableID)
Items can relate to not just several other items but also to several versions of those items. This method provides access to these versions. 1*stableID -> N*relatedStableID -> M*version.

Parameters:
relatedStableID -
Returns:
array of ints corresponding to the versions of the item the relatedStableID refers to.
